  <brief_title>Proximal Humeral Comminuted Fractures in the Elderly - PERCELE Trial</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effectiveness and Cost-effectiveness of Conservative and Operative Treatment of Three- and Four-part Fractures of the Proximal Humerus. A Nested Randomised Controlled Trial and Cohort Study</official_title>
